<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>左玄的个人网页</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007BFF;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .main-content {
            flex: 3;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .sidebar {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .blog, .gallery, .contact {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .contact form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .contact label, .contact input, .contact textarea {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .contact input, .contact textarea {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>左玄的个人网页</h1>
        <p>撰稿人</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#blog">博客</a>
        <a href="#gallery">相册</a>
        <a href="#contact">联系我</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content">
            <section id="blog" class="blog">
                <h2>博客</h2>
                <p>这里是我的博客内容...</p>
            </section>
            <section id="gallery" class="gallery">
                <h2>相册</h2>
                <p>这里是我的相册...</p>
            </section>
            <section id="contact" class="contact">
                <h2>联系我</h2>
                <form action="#" method="post">
                    <label for="name">姓名:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                    <label for="email">电子邮箱:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    <label for="message">留言:</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                    <input type="submit" value="提交">
                </form>
            </section>
        </div>
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <h2>关于我</h2>
            <p>我是左玄，一名热爱写作的撰稿人。</p>
            <h2>联系方式</h2>
            <p>电子邮箱: your-email@example.com</p>
            <p>电话: 123-456-7890</p>
        </aside>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 左玄</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
